---
title: Butternut & Sweet Potato Soup with Bacon Note: Blender Required
description: For this harvest-inspired meal, you’ll whip up a pot of earthy-sweet butternut squash and sweet potato soup with just a touch of nutmeg. Blitz in the blender (required!) until smooth and creamy, then dollop with tangy crême fraîche and a shower of bacon-scallion-panko breadcrumbs for crunchy contrast and serve with garlic-lemon toasts for dipping.
